						<summary>

						<p>Slab in the village.</p>						

						<p>Vijayanagara: Sadāśivadēva.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1481, Siddhārthin, Śrāvana śu. 15,</hi> corresponding to 1559 A.D., July 19, Wednesday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. It registers a grant of land as <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> probably by Gaṅga Vīrappa at the instance of <hi rend="italic">mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Rāmarāju Timmarājayya.</p>						

